<rml>
<head>
  <link type="text/rcss" href="resize_scene.rcss"/>
  <!-- EN: Resize sanity scene (AUD-PUB-1) -- #probe fills the whole viewport
           (width:100%/height:100%, no margin/border/padding), so its border-box
           geometry is a deterministic oracle that must track window resize.
       PT: Cena de sanidade de resize (AUD-PUB-1) -- #probe preenche a viewport
           inteira (width:100%/height:100%, sem margem/borda/padding), então sua
           geometria border-box é um oráculo determinístico que deve acompanhar
           o resize da janela. -->
  <title>glintfx resize sanity</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="probe">&nbsp;</div>
</body>
</rml>
